data.description: Sprawling brick ranch located on a .88 acre corner lot in beautiful Highland Lake Estates. This home boasts over 3600 fin sq. ft. Landscaped  front yard and covered front porch welcome you home. The living room has a gas fireplace & surround sound speakers, as well as patio doors that lead to the back patio (also with speakers). Kitchen boasts a full complement of appliances, pantry, and there is a large eat-in area right off the kitchen. Separate Dining room. Master bedroom is HUGE with a trey ceiling. Jacuzzi tub, walk-in shower, double vanity, & huge walk-in closet grace the master bath. The 1st floor laundry room has a nice utility sink, and a huge storage closet. Finished walk-out basement provides so many possibilities!  The kids can have a space and the adults have room too. Wet bar area has tile floors and a mini fridge. Possible 4th bedroom (non-conforming), and you also have a full bath too! Lots of space for storage. 3 car garage is massive inside w/tall ceilings. Plantation blinds in most rooms.  Upper and lower patios, lake access for fishing, basketball and tennis court access, too!  Great neighbors and neighborhood!  Convenient school bus pick up and drop off.  Radon Mitigation system installed in 2014, underground electric fence for pets, buried propane tank for fireplace and furnace, water softener is owned.
